{"tid":2019883,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩工廠 懷疑違反城規會規劃大綱圖所列地段用途","createTime":"2020-05-16T15:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T16:22:20.000Z","uid":233301,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1875ae00dd01962248b2ab62d06d713fecbbc594","tid":2019883,"uid":233301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jsCZJy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jsCZJy.png&h=ceeb6375&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pm6Tx3z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpm6Tx3z.png&h=77523cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyOq8BV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyOq8BV.png&h=cf94ed0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pGEJVgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpGEJVgW.png&h=4d7ef946&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzbgvQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzbgvQg.png&h=973bd130&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PyO3aQh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyO3aQh.png&h=993485de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMask Factory 懷疑違反城規會規劃大綱圖所列地段用途<br />\n<br />\nMask Factory 位於地段編號DD 125 lot 167, 168, 169, 177, 181RP<br />\n<br />\n假設生產口罩之工廠設於以上地段<br />\n<br />\n該等地段於規劃大綱圖列為「其他指定用途(環保運輸服務停泊及營運設施)」<br />\n<br />\n按大綱圖index，第一、二欄核准用途並無工業/工廠一項，若要於該地段進行工業運作，需向城規會出作更變用途申請，一般需時甚久，除非該地段於很久以前（起碼上年之前）已就用途更變作出申請，否則有機會違反城規會所定立的地段用途<br />\n<br />\n另最好有手足近mapping office既去 check lot index plan確認lot的對應地點，因現時直接係outline zoning plan check有機會出錯地方<br />\n<br />\nLand lease 都可以睇睇"},{"pid":"7734692de8094b003731229c49a0a1b91b7d1956","tid":2019883,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88b674359478e5051ba4f405390df7e073df8463","tid":2019883,"u